   databases, where the data sets represent different level of detail, or
   different point of views for the same geographical features. The
   {ScaleMaster} model makes it possible to formalize how to choose the
   features to map from the different data sets. The paper proposes an
   extension of the {ScaleMaster} model that drives automatic
   generalization rather than guidelines for manual mapmaking. The
